		        <p><strong>1.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;C&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; (th&ocirc;ng tin li&ecirc;n h&#7879; shop v&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&#7841;i di&#7879;n shop) &#273;&#432;&#7907;c y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911;, &#273;&uacute;ng ch&iacute;nh t&#7843;, th&#7889;ng nh&#7845;t v&#7899;i nhau, kh&ocirc;ng vi ph&#7841;m c&aacute;c quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; &#273;&#259;ng tin n&oacute;i chung.</p>
	            <p><strong>2.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;Th&ocirc;ng tin &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; ph&#7843;i trung th&#7921;c, r&otilde; r&agrave;ng, kh&ocirc;ng g&acirc;y nh&#7847;m l&#7851;n ho&#7863;c hi&#7875;u l&#7847;m &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i xem v&#7873; uy t&iacute;n b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng c&#361;ng nh&#432; c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin nh&#7853;n bi&#7871;t kh&aacute;c c&#7911;a shop.</p>
	            <p><strong>3.&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;&#272;&#7883;a ch&#7881; shop ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911;, c&#7909; th&#7875;. Shop &#273;&#7863;t t&#7841;i c&aacute;c trung t&acirc;m th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i, ch&#7907; ph&#7843;i ghi r&otilde; s&#7889; l&ocirc;, s&#7889; qu&#7847;y, s&#7889; t&#7847;ng, v.v&hellip;</p>
