	            <p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;5.2</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;T&ecirc;n c&ocirc;ng ty/th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7843;o h&#7897; ho&#7863;c c&oacute; b&#7843;n quy&#7873;n, c&#7909; th&#7875; nh&#432; sau: Alibaba, Adayroi, Vatgia, Hotdeal, Cungmua, Muachung, Vascara, Lazada, Tiki,&hellip;; PNJ, PANDORA, LV, SAMSUNG, G-STAR, GUCCI, PUMA, Tommy, Tommy Hifiger, PHILIPS, Yves Saint Laurent (YSL), Louis Vuitton, v.v&hellip;</p>
	            <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>5.3</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;S&#7917; d&#7909;ng k&yacute; t&#7921; &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t (@, #, $,*, !, &ldquo;&rdquo;,?, {,},++, ---,v.v&hellip;), hai kho&#7843;ng tr&#7855;ng li&ecirc;n ti&#7871;p tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n, s&#7889; &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i, t&#7915; ng&#7919; ph&#7843;n c&#7843;m, vi ph&#7841;m thu&#7847;n phong m&#7929; t&#7909;c, v&#259;n h&oacute;a v&agrave; ph&aacute;p lu&#7853;t Vi&#7879;t Nam.</p>
