	            <p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>5.5</strong>&nbsp; T&ecirc;n Shop kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;a t&#7915; kh&oacute;a v&#7873; qu&#7843;ng c&aacute;o (nh&#432; khuy&#7871;n m&atilde;i, qu&#7843;ng c&aacute;o,&hellip;) v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;a t&#7915; kh&oacute;a mang t&iacute;nh ch&#7845;t nh&#7841;y c&#7843;m, li&ecirc;n quan &#273;&#7871;n v&#259;n h&oacute;a thu&#7847;n phong m&#7929; t&#7909;c.</p>
